data.description: This is the ONE! This 4 bedroom 3 FULL bath home offers both one floor living with some extra flare! This Ranch/Cape Cod home literally has 2 master bedrooms (with private ensuite bathrooms)- offering one on the main level AND one on the second floor. This 8 years young home has a very convenient and open floor plan. The living room/kitchen combination makes it very easy to entertain! The kitchen has a spacious island with plenty of seating and LOADS of cabinet space. The stainless steel kitchen appliances stay with the home as well. There is also a morning/dining room nestled right off the kitchen.  The 1st floor also has 2 additional bedrooms which share a bathroom and main floor laundry. The 2nd floor has its own living area, bedroom and bathroom! The basement is HUGE and is plumbed for a bathroom (there is also a stand alone sink for water access)! It won't take much at all to finish it as it already has some drywall, insulation and electrical! This home is located close to major highways  making for a convenient commute! Qualified buyers could take advantage of down payment assistance opportunities! Make sure you schedule your showing TODAY!
